+Tech Description: The old Angel scout fighter is second only to the Apollo in length of service and number of kills. Developed as an interceptor/reconnaissance fighter in the first years of the Terran-Vasudan War, it also made a formidable match for the PVF Anubis and other early Vasudan fighters. Upgrades to the Apollo have made the Angel largely obsolete, and the original design has since been retired in favor of its successor, the GTF Valkyrie. 
$end_multi_text 
