$Name:				PVS Scarab
$Short name:		VSup
$Species:			Vasudan
+Tech Description:
The Scarab is very similar to our Centaur: We believe the Vasudans stole the design of this ship from us.  It is used for in flight rearming of fighters and bombers.  In longer engagements, these ships can mean the difference between victory and defeat.  The major difference between this ship and the Centaur is that the Scarab is unmanned.
$end_multi_text
