$Name:				SB Shaitan
$Short name:		SBomb1
$Species:			Shivan
+Tech Description:
The Shaitan bomber is only slightly superior to our own bombers - it's shielding is better, but its capacity seems to be far worse.  Perhaps the Shivans were so assured that they would only need one payload to destroy a target.
We consider the Shaitan to be a Class C threat.
$end_multi_text
